We are looking into your query and will reply in line with the provisions of the EBRD’s Access to Information Policy. 
The Bank will normally respond within 20 working days after receiving the request or clarification or, if a timely explanation for a further delay is provided (within 10 working days following receipt), no later than 40 working days.

You will receive a response if your query is related to EBRD operations.
For job vacancies and procurement enquiries, we kindly direct you to the EBRD Careers Website and EBRD Procurement Notices, respectively. 
Please refer to the recently released EBRD Consultation Hub for the opportunity to review and provide feedback on all upcoming EBRD country and sectoral strategies and institutional policies during open consultation periods. 

Kind regards,
